POINTS_FLAT_CONJUNCTION - bauernhof.preset.card.EffectType
The effect evaluates to Card.getBaseValue() if the player has ALL cards in Effect.getSelector() on their hand, otherwise 0.
POINTS_FLAT_DISJUNCTION - bauernhof.preset.card.EffectType
The effect evaluates to Card.getBaseValue() if the player has ANY card in Effect.getSelector() on their hand, otherwise 0.
POINTS_FOREACH - bauernhof.preset.card.EffectType
The effect evaluates to Effect.getEffectValue() times the number of cards in Effect.getSelector() that the player has on their hand.
POINTS_SUM_BASEVALUES - bauernhof.preset.card.EffectType
The effect evaluates to the sum of Card.getBaseValue() of each card in Effect.getSelector() that the player has on their hand.
